vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of Paris Street also known as Parris Street to RP Wentworth, LLC, the abutting owner, containing approximately 18,288 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Taylor Street and Good Latimer Expressway; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Capital Reserve Fund ($1,159,576.00) General Fund ($20,000.00), plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
